Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.79,0:00:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:00:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.19,0:01:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Varon from the Three Musketeers of Doma...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His Dueling strategy is far from incomplete!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His attacks strike me one after the other...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My body aches... and my insides are tearing apart...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'm not so weak that I'd be finished with a few shots like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I want to get Mai back and defeat Doma at their own game...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't allow myself to be defeated by the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Reverbarating Soul"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you connected!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm so at my limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go look for Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just calm down, Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you randomly search the streets, you'll only waste time and energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not just that Varon punk who's after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai's also out there looking for Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... If he ends up fighting with Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} can't fight Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He knows what will happen if he clashes with Mai again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be settled so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it! Jounouchi's location!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, let's see... he should be downtown!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys go to find the safest spot you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to search for Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Take me along, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu... Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otogi, sorry... but I need you to stay with Rebecca and Professor Hopkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Take me along wit-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is as far as we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't afford to slow them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca... Can I ask you to have faith in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will save my Partner, no matter what I have to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better come back here safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be responsible for their safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:03:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get a move on, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be carefull, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is no longer lost in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just believe in him... in the other Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything is now up to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Save this world, Nameless Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Save my Darling, Other Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm staking everything on this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That card...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Rifleman of Landstar in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I activate the Magic Card, Resurrection of the Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Monster I'm bringing back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rocket Warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Claw of Hermos!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally got out here, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Come at me with all you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the moment I beat you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will achieve the ultimate victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It... should be somewhere around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi! You better be safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the effect of the Claw of Hermos, I fuse him with Rocket Warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rocket Hermos Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I equip it to Rifleman of Landstar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It combined?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something outside of my Armor Monsters is capable of that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go wetting yourself just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Rifleman of Landstar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack, Rocket Hermos Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy all the enemies in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bracing for impact of enemy attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Changing to defensive armor for damage absorption!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:06:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I get him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Booyah! I beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why didn't the boundary disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure felt that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd expect no less from the power of Hermos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why? I attacked you directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you certainly nailed me good there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't have you forgetting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...about Active Guard's Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's because I've got {\i0}this{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This Active Guard holds an Effect that makes all battle damage received on my end reduced to zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a {\i1}shame{\i0} it is, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I broke that {\i1}impregnable{\i0} armor of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure did, but in exchange, I got my hands on something {\i1}nice{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something "nice"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on the Rocket Hermos Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Data Brain ain't your average Equipment Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever the Monster this card\N was equipped to is destroyed by the opponent's magic effects,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this card shows its {\i1}true{\i0} ambitious effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir! It copies that same magic effect so I can use it for {\i1}myself{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using {\i1}that{\i0} Special Effect on my Standby Phase,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Pyshic Armor Head from the Cemetery in Attack Position!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then{\i0} I Summon my Burning Knuckle Armor in Attack Position!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Burning Knuckle Armor, for every Armor Monster on the field, it receives a 200 Attack Power boost!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Afterwards{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This here's a pretty sweet lookin' weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna give it a test drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blow 'em all to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rocket Hermos Cannon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what a weapon created from the Legendary Dragons is all about!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Tis a pity I can only use it for {\i1}one{\i0} turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How you feelin', Jounouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being shot at with your own weapon and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think you'll be able to get back on your feet before your Life Points drop to zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I doubt you'll be able to fight for much longer with the state your body's in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say to giving up and making it easier on yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said this from the start, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I ain't runnin'...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how bad the situation may be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never give up until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's not afraid of my attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've never met anyone who could put up a front like him...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So this... is the man Mai's been chasing after for the "truth"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still rarin' and ready to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where we start the battle for {\i1}real{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Varon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Let's go, Mokuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now {\i1}hold{\i0} it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth are you people doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just bought this car!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This should cover it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Bought"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, you Doma punks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Critias was resonating just earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did something happen to the deadbeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I have no time to worry about others right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait right there, Dartz.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to shove that pathetic plan of yours right down your throat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I use it... one more time... I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I place one reverse card face-down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you couldn't even manage to Summon a single Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This useless resistance of yours is wasted effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be it a Trap, be it a Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy it with all my strength!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Black Hole Shield Armor in Attack Position!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This increases Burning Knuckle's Attack Power even {\i1}further{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Opposing player's field: Zero Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One reverse card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Probability of being Trap Card: 50%.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it {\i1}is{\i0} a trap, I only know how to {\i1}attack{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I attack with Burning Knuckle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct Attack Jounouchi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This... {\i1}ends{\i0} it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activated a Trap Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Trap Card, Aura Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...! That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Level Four Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Attack Power: 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to fight the same way you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aura Armor activates when I take a Direct Attack while I have 2000 Life Points or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By halving my Life Points, I negate that damage...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I get to Special Summon a "Monster"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's what this here is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can attach itself to the player just like my Armor Monsters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}different{\i0} than your Armor Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its Attack and Defense Points are equal to the player's Life Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In brazen terms, if I fall, I {\i1}lose{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simple enough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, so I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, whoever remains standing wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That what you meant?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a reverse card!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My Timaeus responded to Hermos.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did something happen to Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please be safe, Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roll of Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the effects of Roll of Fate,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I draw cards equal to the result of the die roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then discard the same number of cards from the top of my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What did he get...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this! I activate a Ritual Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red-Eyes Transmigration!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to sacrifice Red-Eyes Black Dragon along with a Warrior-Type Monster from my hand or on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a {\i1}Ritual Magic{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use this Red-Eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...along with the Aura Armor attached to me... Or in otherwords, I sacrifice {\i1}myself{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord of the Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What{\i0}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes! I attack Psychic Armor Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this... decides the match!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Hole Shield!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord of the Red's attack...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its Special Ability activates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By sacrificing Black Hole Shield, all damage done to the player is reduced to zero!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had that thing beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barely made it out in tact...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm shaking...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Me...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I actually {\i0}afraid{\i1} of the bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:17:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's been so long since I've felt like this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've never felt such a passionate desire to grind someone into the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuya Jounouchi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best! My fight with you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here! I'm getting pumped up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a real Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad I have to fight you under these circumstances!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go acting on your own, Varon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} Jounouchi's opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Switch with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to fight Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move along, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way in hell I'd switch places with someone when I'm enjoying this Duel so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's {\i1}you{\i0}, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Varon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you're so bent on pursuing Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally began to understand\N while Dueling him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He holds something we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what it is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To face one another in a Duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with a genuine straight-forward passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have that ability, do we...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Varon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Let's get on with it, Jounouchi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one reverse card!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card! Resurrection of the Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to resurrect...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buster Pyle!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this attack makes it through, I {\i1}win{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa there! Allow {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scapegoat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really think your little {\i1}sheep{\i0} can block my {\i1}fists{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't play my Scapegoats so I can hide behind them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord of the Red's Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If two Magics are used in the same turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...after the second Magic is activated, I can destroy all Monsters on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Second"...? You {\i1}didn't{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! {\i1}Your{\i0} Magic Card, Resurrection of the Dead, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No you {\i1}don't{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buster Pyle!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never expected my invincible Armor to be shattered...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's still more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have more of my Life Points left!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it, Jounouchi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go, Varon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct Attack!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Extinction Fist!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card automatically ends a Ritual Monster's Battle Phase!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, I return the assault!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Extinction Fist!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord of the... Red...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Varon and Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whichever one of them wins... it'll be decided with just one more strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:22:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.54,0:22:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.15,0:22:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.22,0:22:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.98,0:22:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.88,0:22:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.03,0:23:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.55,0:23:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.58,0:23:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Admist a painful and emotional battle, Jounouchi and Varon have come to understand one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}'s the only one they're seeing now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.55,0:23:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But both their health and Life Points are at their limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than likely, this next attack will decide the match!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then Varon brings out his Full Armor once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pitting their last bit of strength into their fists,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which one of them will remain standing in the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, what will Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.60,0:23:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The End of a Painful Battle"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
